## UseFrom type

All of TOrigin except Key from TUse

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
export declare type UseFrom<TOrigin, TUse, Key extends keyof TUse> = Pick<TOrigin, Exclude<keyof TOrigin, Key>> & Pick<TUse, Key>;
```
